[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":77},["ShallowReactive",2],{"tag-gong-ju-1":3,"footer-config":48},{"code":4,"message":5,"data":6,"timestamp":47},200,"查询成功",{"total":7,"records":8},2,[9,34],{"id":10,"title":11,"slug":12,"summary":13,"coverImage":14,"category":15,"tags":16,"viewCount":25,"likeCount":26,"commentCount":27,"isTop":28,"isFeatured":28,"publishTime":29,"createTime":30,"author":31},72,"图文详解 Claude Code 从入门到精通（一）：Claude Code 的安装与启动","claude-code-installation-startup","Claude Code是Anthropic推出的AI编程命令行工具，专为开发者提供终端内AI协作工作流。本文作为系列入门指南的第一篇，重点介绍其安装与启动流程。文章详细说明了系统要求，包括操作系统、Node.js版本和网络条件，并提供了原生安装和包管理器安装两种方法。针对国内用户，推荐使用智谱GLM Coding Plan以获得更稳定的网络体验和更高性价比，同时给出了具体的配置步骤和模型切换方法。","https://cdn.icybean.cn//blog/images/2026/03/11/bdeb2293470b4f4486fab3b85d212eb8",null,[17,21],{"id":18,"name":19,"slug":20},19,"工具","gong-ju",{"id":22,"name":23,"slug":24},20,"技术","ji-shu",21,5,0,1,"2026-03-11T16:47:25","2026-03-11T15:57:25",{"id":28,"nickname":32,"avatar":33},"icybean","https://cdn.icybean.cn/%E5%A4%B4%E5%83%8F_wiki-small.png",{"id":35,"title":36,"slug":37,"summary":38,"coverImage":39,"category":15,"tags":40,"viewCount":43,"likeCount":26,"commentCount":27,"isTop":28,"isFeatured":28,"publishTime":44,"createTime":45,"author":46},70,"保姆级教程：手把手教你如何使用FlClash科学上网","flclash-tutorial","FlClash是一款基于Flutter开发的跨平台Clash图形客户端，用于解决访问GitHub等国外网站时遇到的网络问题。它通过规则匹配智能分流，国内网站直连，国外网站走代理。使用前需关闭其他加速器软件，并获取代理订阅链接。本文提供了从注册购买订阅、下载安装客户端到配置FlClash的详细步骤，帮助用户实现科学上网。","https://cdn.icybean.cn//blog/images/2026/03/08/829cb16dc4484cceab7b7bf73fb77177.png",[41,42],{"id":18,"name":19,"slug":20},{"id":22,"name":23,"slug":24},36,"2026-03-08T11:36:56","2026-03-08T11:36:55",{"id":28,"nickname":32,"avatar":33},1773648689637,{"code":4,"message":49,"data":50,"timestamp":76},"操作成功",{"site":51,"feature":60,"social":62,"extras":68},{"title":52,"subtitle":53,"description":54,"keywords":55,"author":56,"avatar":33,"favicon":57,"icp":58,"policeBeian":59},"我的技术博客","记录学习，分享技术","专注Java、Spring Boot、前端等技术分享，记录学习笔记和开发经验","Java,Spring Boot,前